{
  "stem": "2833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the few young people who had, you know, been left in Prague, we always went to my girlfriend's house, because they had the largest room where we could all kind of lie down on the floor and stay overnight.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we all became very, very close-- but especially Margot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, they asked for-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --four-- well, in my case, in one little village in Czechoslovakia, they had asked for two men and two women to come and do labor on the field.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was 1940.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went with one young man, and my girlfriend went with another young man to that little town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we worked in the fields and in the house, you know, taking care of animals, and of cows, and so on; and were there for two months, and did labor for-- for the farmers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they sent us back to Prague again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then shortly after that, they started with transport-- 1941.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I stayed in Prague till December '41.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I went to Terezin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they sent us a postcard to come on a certain day with 30 kilo of luggage, including bedding, food, clothing, everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And come to a-- it's a big hall of-- exhibition hall, I would-- I think it's called.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we went there-- my mother, her sister-- who was still with us-- and me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stayed there for about three days and were registered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, we had to give them the key to our apartment, which we had left with everything in it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it took a few days to get us-- three days, I think-- to get us ready.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
